<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- css ex -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/home.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/navbar.css" />

    <!-- cdn fontawsome -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    />

    <!-- cdn fontgoogle -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>myPersonal - Website</title>

    <!-- cdn bootstrap -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light p-nav">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
        <img
          src="assets/image/image.png"
          alt="logo-dumbways"
          width="30"
          height="30"
          class="d-inline-block align-top"
        />
      </a>
      <button
        class="navbar-toggler"
        type="button"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#navbarNav"
        aria-controls="navbarNav"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-label="Toggle navigation"
      >
        <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
          <li class="nav-item active text-black">
            <a class="nav-link font-weight-bold" href="/">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link color text-dark" href="project"> My Project</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" href="testimoni">Testimoni</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        {{#if isLogin}}
          <i class="mr-lg-2 ml-auto fa fa-user"></i>
          <span class="mr-lg-4 font-weight-bold">{{username}}</span>
          <form
            method="post"
            action="/logout"
            class="m-0 p-0 d-inline-block mr-3"
          >
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="btn btn-danger btn-sm m-0 w-100"
            >Logout</button>
          </form>
        {{else}}
          <a href="/login" class="mr-lg-3 ml-auto">Login</a>
        {{/if}}
        <a href="contactMe" class=""><button
            class="btn btn-primary cont w-100 contactMe-button"
          >
            contact me
          </button></a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- main -->
    <div class="containerEX">
      <div>
        <h1 class="mb-4">Halo, selamat datang!</h1>
        <p class="">
          Saya lulusan Fisika dari Universitas Negeri Semarang, dengan fokus
          pada fisika komputasi. Saya memiliki keterampilan analitis yang kuat
          dan pemahaman yang mendalam tentang teori fisika yang mendukung
          aplikasi komputasi. Saya sangat bersemangat untuk mengembangkan
          keterampilan dan pengetahuan saya dalam bidang komputasi di lingkungan
          kerja. Saat ini, saya sedang menjalani bootcamp untuk menjadi seorang
          Fullstack Developer. Dengan keahlian dalam HTML, CSS, Python, MySQL,
          dan JavaScript, saya siap untuk menghadapi tantangan dalam
          pengembangan perangkat lunak.
        </p>

        <div class="cardCVDownload">
          <a href="contactMe" class="linkContact"><button
              class="contactButton item"
            >contact</button></a>
          <!-- wadah penyimpanan elemen contact -->
          <div class="CV-container">
            <a
              href="assets/cv/CV ADIT DWI RAMADHAN.pdf"
              class="text-dark"
              target="_blank"
            >download CV
              <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- wadah penyimpanan icon icon -->
        <div class="iconContainer item">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i>
          <i class="fa-brands fa-square-instagram"></i>
          <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
          <i class="fa-brands fa-square-x-twitter"></i>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- wadah penyimpanan card -->
      <div class="card item">
        <img src="assets/image/foto formal sidang.jpg" />
        <div class="mt-3">
          <h3 class="text-center">Adit Dwi Ramadhan</h3>
          <p class="text-center">Fullstack Developer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{#if isLogin}}
      <div class="containerEX w-80 h-100" style="display: block !important;">
        <h1 class="text-center mx-auto mb-5">list my project</h1>
        <a href="/project">
          <table class="table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">#</th>
                <th scope="col">Name Author</th>
                <th scope="col">Name Project</th>
                <th scope="col">Created At</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {{#each myProject as |myProject index|}}
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row">{{index}}</th>
                  <td>{{myProject.author_name}}</td>
                  <td>{{myProject.name}}</td>
                  <td>{{myProject.createdAt}}</td>
                </tr>
              {{/each}}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </a>
      </div>
    {{/if}}

    <script src="assets/js/navbar.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>